text: "Beautiful Nebraska" is the regional anthem of the U.S. state of Nebraska. The music was composed by Jim Fras in 1960 and the lyrics were written by Jim Fras and Guy G. Miller, prior to adoption as Nebraska's state song in 1967.https://www.netstate.com/states/symb/songs/ne_beautiful_ne.htm ==References== Category:Symbols of Nebraska Nebraska Category:Music of Nebraska
title: Beautiful Nebraska
